metadata.name: The BoldType Genesis Collection - Thales
metadata.description: Boldness is the beginning of action, but fortune controls how it ends (Democritus). The BoldType Collection is dedicated to all the fortunate who are taking upon themselves to lend to the misfortunate and to aid them and to favor them, then is there pity and no isolation but companionship and mutual defense and concord among the citizens and other good things too many to catalogue.Boldness is the beginning of action, but fortune controls how it ends (Democritus).
